[{\"slug\":\"airbrush-makeup-florida-brides\",\"title\":\"Why Airbrush Makeup Is a Game-Changer for Florida Brides\",\"date\":\"2026-03-06T19:11:12.718Z March 6, 2026\",\"category\":\"Bridal\",\"excerpt\":\"Discover why airbrush makeup is the top choice for brides getting married in Florida's heat and humidity.\",\"content\":\"Florida's tropical climate can be a beautiful backdrop for a wedding, but heat and humidity are real challenges for bridal makeup. Airbrush application creates a ultra-thin, breathable layer of foundation that bonds to the skin and resists sweat, moisture, and tears far better than traditional makeup. For Fort Lauderdale brides, this means flawless, camera-ready coverage that lasts from the first look all the way through the last dance.\"}]